pr_body:
This PR implements the following feature to OpenPIP:
- Added organism create in data section.
- Added organism delete in data section. 
- Added data upload, specific to a particular organism.
- Added organism level search of proteins. 
- Added organism info section in search tab.
- Added test data files to test upload. 
- Simplified deploying OpenPIP in local instance.
- Updated readme and install guide.
